Detailed Description

template<class Value, class Key, class DiscardFunction, class HashFunction, class KeyEqual, class KeyExtract, class Allocator>
class mm::cache_table< Value, Key, DiscardFunction, HashFunction, KeyEqual, KeyExtract, Allocator >

CacheTable: back-end data structure class.

This class should not be used directly. Instead use one of CacheMap or CacheSet.
